"lyricsSc": "我的爸爸 我感谢你 为了我的幸福 默默地付出 你是上帝赐给我的礼物 让我为你祝福 愿你平安 有你在的地方 就是我的家 谢谢你的肩膀 扛起所有重担 有你在的地方 充满着温暖 因着爱 绽放光芒 我的妈妈 我答应妳 记得妳的叮咛 不让妳挂心 若我跌倒 会勇敢站起来 让妳充满笑容 引以为傲 有妳在的地方 就是我的家 谢谢妳的坚强 给我生命榜样 有妳在的地方 充满着温暖 因着爱 绽放光芒 是你让我学会 看见生命美好 因着爱 我们绽放光芒",
"englishLyrics": "My dearest dad, I want to say thank you. For my sake, you gave your everything for me. You are a gift that God has given me. May your life be blessed with joy and peace.\nHome is where the heart is, home is where you are. Thank you for always carrying my burdens. Home is where the heart is, filled with warmth and love. For your love glows in my heart.\nMy dearest mom, I will promise you, all that you have taught me, keep it in my heart. And when I fall, I’ll stand up once again. You don’t have to worry, I’ll make you proud.\nHome is where the heart is, home is where you are. You have been my strength, the one that I look up to. Home is where the heart is, filled with warmth and love. For your love glows in my heart.\nYou’re the one who taught me to see the beauty of life. With your love, we will let our light shine. ————————————————————————————————————————"
