"lyricsSc": "我抬头仰望\n帮助我的神\n在患难之中\n大水四起\n\n祢提拔我\n到安稳之地\n\n我抬头仰望\n帮助我的神\n过死荫幽谷\n疲惫之处\n\n祢引领我\n到安歇之处\n\n主祢是我藏身之处\n护庇我\n藏我在翅膀荫下\n主\n祢同在是我得救的乐歌\n环绕我\n坚定我\n隐藏我\n当行的路\n祢与我同行\n纵然前方\n仇敌埋伏\n主祢是我\n藏身之处 我倚靠祢\n定睛在祢\n大水四起\n坚定不移\n必有恩惠慈爱\n四面环绕 义人都因祢的\n应许欢欣",
"englishLyrics": "I lift my eyes. Lord, You are my help. When troubles come, thunders and floods, You pick me up, and lead me to peace.\nI lift my eyes. Lord, You are my help. Through valleys of death, through weariness, You're guiding me to greener pastures.\nLord, You are my hiding place. Cover me, hide me in Your wings of grace. Lord, Your presence is my strength and my song. Surround me, strengthen me, hide me, Lord. [RAP] The road ahead, You're walking with me. Even though my foes are ahead. Lord, You are my hiding place.\nRely in You, focus on You, floods from all sides, steadfast in You. Kindness and mercy are surrounding me. The righteous rejoice in Your promises, sheesh. ————————————————————————————————————————"
